Introduction

Morethan7 (Korean: 모어댄7; Japanese: モアダン7) is a duo consisting of The Deep, and Crack Bit. They debuted on June 28, 2019 with the single Beautiful Garden. They are assumed to be disbanded as their instagram account was deleted.
